{"tid":422474,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"成人台嗰拃咸濕仔真係好撚嘔心","createTime":"2017-10-03T05:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T15:41:36.000Z","uid":81684,"like":513,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"6db7c4688ca8329f86398c96aa5710fced2ad742","tid":422474,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:45:14.000Z","msg":"啲內文仲嘔心過其他forum啲咸濕佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜撚嘢招女奴 招sp 仲有自貼賓周相嗰啲post<br />\n成班狗公簡直唔撚知醜<br />\n平時班毒撚喺度話自己樣ok已經醜怪㗎啦<br />\n屌你連自己碌鳩都要攞嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後成班麻甩佬喺度圍爐取暖 好撚核突呀大佬<br />\n唔洗add都估到係啲現實溝唔到女嘅自大毒撚仔<br />\n係咁撚正嘅去轉老蘭大撚把閪屌 屌撚到唔想屌啦<br />\n洗撚咁兜踎喺度開完post自己推post咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日以為自己好撚正 條嘢好撚堅 好多女想比佢屌比佢調教<br />\n慳啲啦仆街 現實咪又係籮底橙 扮乜撚嘢大把女屌啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢班核突佬正正就係最撚自戀嗰拃<br />\n成日以為啲女見到自己碌嘢就出水<br />\n好心咪撚咁睇得起自己啦 做雞就話無得揀客啫<br />\n正常女人都唔撚吼呢拃廢柴毒撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算有女送上門 咪又係豬閪臭雞物以類聚<br />\n睇怕成世都要食啲下欄嘢<br />\n然後眼看啲有錢佬拖撚住條高檔貨色<br />\n自己就幾十歲人仲喺度等免費雞運到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為自己有得揀 都唔撚睇下自己乜撚嘢條件<br />\n現實就係佢地望人一眼對方都會覺得猥瑣噁心<br />\n莫講話現實啦 我隔撚住個mon都聞到浸毒撚除啦<br />\n偏偏班柒窮厹毒撚就係咁撚唔知醜<br />\n攞命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a2e0e75d73fe9f15aff3c6148ac1f3322f5723","tid":422474,"uid":41737,"like":10,"dislike":76,"score":-66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:52:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5df9018dcf59b7f5096e2ff8e6f9c35587b0264","tid":422474,"uid":81684,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咪繼續開post屌佢地囉 <br />\n人地約到大把淫絲出黎做愛 理撚得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰班臭雞 隨便攞去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee37061a4e83175e0a55ca27067e3ef0d702330","tid":422474,"uid":59221,"like":59,"dislike":3,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:02:13.000Z","msg":"果班柒頭低質到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前開依d招友招性奴post一定比人屌到仆街<br />\n依家竟然開到咁多個都冇事<br />\n叫雞都算 成班網上招fd子真係好撚噁心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764aabc0a53632a757bc31c6e27f1bbeb1d57f18","tid":422474,"uid":5649,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"貼撚真係好低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed639ef4e9db0243e82e38156343c21469a145d","tid":422474,"uid":81684,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果班柒頭低質到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前開依d招友招性奴post一定比人屌到仆街<br />\n依家竟然開到咁多個都冇事<br />\n叫雞都算 成班網上招fd子真係好撚噁心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成個成人台比班厹毒撚搞到烏煙瘴氣<br />\n變咗發情台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7329f7408d8fda02f664fdab1e74e747deb61ee0","tid":422474,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:11:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貼撚真係好低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貼完撚仲要留tg<br />\n仲唔要面過mk仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a26f8ed679c63115622f30e64e7d95247c89bcc0","tid":422474,"uid":11598,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲tg group先過癮<br />\n開果個因為入唔到之前人哋開個啲<br />\n就自己開過個，講到咩1：1男女平衡乜乜物物<br />\n屌你其實就係filter走晒啲仔<br />\n後來入唔到果啲仔又心郁郁自己開過個無限loop<br />\n真係好撚on9"},{"pid":"7785787e0b864dd5669bfee87e18c22930d35d22","tid":422474,"uid":81684,"like":0,"di