s=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67e9eff215fa3a4e247c2272334f207803ccf4f","tid":422474,"uid":81684,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慘得過真係有班姣閪落答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果個咩淫絲post個個係到搵食 食完呢個食另一個</blockquote><br />\n難怪啲毒撚係女都話雞 又講咩送比我都唔屌<br />\n原來咁多賤貨做爛市影衰其他女人<br />\n呢啲臭閪浸豬籠就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146c58b1146c36e37eaaef7b9bc889590659876c","tid":422474,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"好心你條死毒撚咪阻鳩人post撚圖啦，你屌乜都得，你屌佢地post撚圖就唔得！"},{"pid":"36247bd8cee6c973ed2bfeb20dc3e7f3b9c31ae3","tid":422474,"uid":20696,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"勁撚嘔心，之前見過一個招sp嘅po，成300個cm入面得兩個女人，其他全部都係男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無飢渴到咁撚樣，喺到list曬自己啲條件出黎「跪求」絲打pm，肉唔肉酸啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔講以為上咗啲咩上鴨網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日話女人係雞係公廁，成人台班用條撚諗野嘅男人仲公廁啦，仲要係一排排棟喺到俾人揀都無人想去嘅臭尿兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw招sp嘅無聊男人定女人都好撚嘔心污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e865e4eee04134be6fbdb8c4d5896ae6e6ad8cf0","tid":422474,"uid":20130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好心你條死毒撚咪阻鳩人post撚圖啦，你屌乜都得，你屌佢地post撚圖就唔得！</blockquote><br />\n期待遲d進化到post射精圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gi